import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Section from './Section'
import AboutUs from './AboutUs'
import Member from './Member'
import Mission from './Mission'

function Home() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Switch>
                <Route path="/about-us">
                    <AboutUs />
                </Route>
                <Route path="/mission">
                    <Mission />
                </Route>
                <Route path="/member">
                    <Member />
                </Route>
                <Route path="/">
                    <Section />
                </Route>
            </Switch>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Home

const Container = styled.div`
    height: 100vh;
`
